trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of resource referenced by a parsed virtual path.
trans-unit.target: 指定剖析的虛擬路徑所參考之資源的型別。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType> enumeration describes the type of resource referenced by a virtual path.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType>列舉描述類型的虛擬路徑所參照的資源。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType> is determined from the parsed extension of the resource.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType>決定從已剖析的延伸模組的資源。

trans-unit.source: Page and control developers do not use the <xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType> enumeration directly.
trans-unit.target: 不使用頁面和控制項的開發人員<xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType>直接列舉型別。

trans-unit.source: Extensibility developers might use the <xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType> enumeration when extending the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageParserFilter> class and overriding its <xref:System.Web.UI.PageParserFilter.AllowVirtualReference%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 擴充性開發人員可能會使用<xref:System.Web.UI.VirtualReferenceType>列舉型別擴充時<xref:System.Web.UI.PageParserFilter>類別而且覆寫其<xref:System.Web.UI.PageParserFilter.AllowVirtualReference%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The parsed virtual path references a master page file.
trans-unit.target: 剖析的虛擬路徑參考主版頁面檔案。

trans-unit.source: The parsed virtual path references a resource that is not an ASP.NET page, master page, user control, or language-specific code file.
trans-unit.target: 剖析的虛擬路徑所參考的資源不是 ASP.NET 網頁、主版頁面、使用者控制項或語言特定的程式碼檔案。

trans-unit.source: The parsed virtual path references an ASP.NET page.
trans-unit.target: 剖析的虛擬路徑參考 ASP.NET 網頁。

trans-unit.source: The parsed virtual path references a code file that is compiled using a specific language compiler.
trans-unit.target: 剖析的虛擬路徑所參考的程式碼檔是使用特定語言編譯器編譯的。

trans-unit.source: The parsed virtual path references an ASP.NET user control.
trans-unit.target: 剖析的虛擬路徑參考 ASP.NET 使用者控制項。
